        "title": "Risk Management: Definition & Components"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-0-f-0",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-0",
        "title": "Risk management is understanding potential costs associated with all behaviors."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-0-f-1",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-0",
        "title": "Risk avoidance means eliminating risks entirely."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-0-f-2",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-0",
        "title": "Risk reduction aims to minimize risks through proactive measures."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-1",
        "parent": "t-applications-0",
        "title": "Legal Framework for Risk Management: Civil Law vs Common Law"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-1-f-0",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-1",
        "title": "Civil Law focuses on codified rules and established procedures."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-1-f-1",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-1",
        "title": "Common Law relies on precedent-based judicial rulings."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-1-f-2",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-1",
        "title": "Understanding the legal framework influences risk management decisions."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-2",
        "parent": "t-applications-0",
        "title": "Risk Avoidance: Minimizing Potential Costs"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-2-f-0",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-2",
        "title": "Understanding legal frameworks is crucial for business decisions."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-2-f-1",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-2",
        "title": "Risk avoidance involves minimizing potential costs through various strategies like eliminating or reducing risk."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-2-f-2",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-2",
        "title": "Risk acceptance involves living with the potential consequences of certain risks."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-3",
        "parent": "t-applications-0",
        "title": "Risk Reduction: Shifting Responsibility and Mitigation Strategies"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-4",
        "parent": "t-applications-0",
        "title": "Risk Acceptance: Weighing Benefits and Risks"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-4-f-0",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-4",
        "title": "Risk acceptance involves choosing to live with potential risks if their impact is considered manageable."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-4-f-1",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-4",
        "title": "Understanding legal frameworks and their implications is crucial for informed decision-making in business."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-applications-0-s-4-f-2",
        "parent": "t-applications-0-s-4",
        "title": "Different approaches exist for managing risk, including avoidance, reduction, shifting, and acceptance."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-0",
