        "title": "Legal Risks"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-0-f-0",
        "parent": "t-overview-0-s-0",
        "title": "**Identify potential legal risks** to your business, including liability and possibility of lawsuits."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-0-f-1",
        "parent": "t-overview-0-s-0",
        "title": "**Evaluate the likelihood and costs** associated with those risks."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-0-f-2",
        "parent": "t-overview-0-s-0",
        "title": "**Consider constitutional rights and limitations**  during any legal decision."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-1",
        "parent": "t-overview-0",
        "title": "Sources of Law"
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-1-f-0",
        "parent": "t-overview-0-s-1",
        "title": "**The Constitution:** Sets fundamental rules for Canadian society."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-1-f-1",
        "parent": "t-overview-0-s-1",
        "title": "**Criminal Law & Tort Law:** Different legal avenues exist for addressing wrongs and potential lawsuits."
      },
      {
        "id": "t-overview-0-s-1-f-2",
        "parent": "t-overview-0-s-1",
        "title": "**Division of Powers:**  Federal vs. Provincial authority defines jurisdiction."
      },
      {
